<chapter line="1">Rudhādayo</chapter>
<hangnum line="2" number="101"></hangnum>
<gatha1 line="3"> Rudhi āvaraṇe muca mocane rica recane,</gatha1>
<gathalast line="4">Sica seke yuja yoge bhuja pālanabhojane;</gathalast>
<hangnum line="5" number="102"></hangnum>
<gatha1 line="6"> Katicchede chidi dvedhākaraṇe bhida vidāraṇe</gatha1>
<gatha2 line="7">Vida lābhe lupacchede vināse lipalimpane</gatha2>
<gathalast line="8">Pisa saṃcuṇṇane hisi vihiṃsāyaṃ (rudhādayo;)</gathalast>
